[16.029, "o", "Here are all exported functions in this project (under `src/`):\r\n\r\n| Function | File | Line |\r\n|---|---|---|\r\n| `isValidEmail` | `src/schemas/user.ts` | 11 |\r\n| `authMiddleware` | `src/middleware/auth.ts` | 8 |\r\n\r\nThere's also one default export:\r\n- `router` (Express router) — `src/routes/auth.ts:37`\r\n\r\nThe remaining exports are type/interface declarations (`CreateUserInput`, `LoginInput`, `UserPayload`, `AuthenticatedRequest`) and a re-export of `authMiddleware` from `src/middleware/index.ts`.\r\n"]
